data.description: Welcome to your beautifully remodeled dream home at 26 Quinn St in Stafford, CT! This stunning property boasts a comprehensive renovation, including new electric from the pole, updated plumbing throughout, and a garage and breezeway/family room rebuilt from the foundation up. The 40-year roof, new siding, and the addition of a deck and patio provide a fresh and inviting exterior. Inside, enjoy the abundance of natural light and energy efficiency with Harvey windows, while the R40 insulation in the attic keeps you comfortable year-round. The second floor features refinished red oak floors, adding a touch of elegance to the space. The breezeway is a highlight with its vaulted ceiling and exposed beam, complemented by recessed lighting throughout the home. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring a marble look quartz countertop, new appliances, and stylish cabinets. This is the perfect place to create culinary masterpieces and entertain guests. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own - it's the epitome of modern living with all the latest updates and a dash of timeless charm. Schedule a viewing today!
